    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The powertrain benefits from a recent VANOS service, ensuring optimal variable valve timing and throttle response across the powerband. Performance is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential and a rigid chassis that has undergone a preventative subframe inspection. While the vehicle displays minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and suspension geometry remain tight, offering a pure analog driving experience with the characteristic rasp of the M-tuned exhaust.",
