    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it runs like a dream and looks great too. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable vehicle that won\u2019t let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
