      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the marque\u2019s high-revving peak. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a serviced Double VANOS system for precision timing across the powerband. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers tactile engagement, routing power through a functional limited-slip differential. Maintenance is up to date, including essential rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the communicative feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering that define this chassis. While showing honest cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, its performance vitals remain sharp and track-ready.",
